overview: Plant one green city boy among a bumper crop of hard and healthy ranch hands. Add a sexually mature foreman, and you've got one hell of a spread where anything will grow! And when the plantin' & plowin' is over, then it's harvest time for these dudes to start pullin' the fruits of their labor at Dude Ranch.
tagline: This city boy finds out what plantin' and plowin' is all about on this XXX farm.
title: Dude Ranch
